            </div>
            <h3><strong>Style guide</strong></h3>
            <h4 style="font-weight: normal">I created a style guide to be more consistent and efficient while working with Figma. Also during creating a style guide I felt the importance to keep it clear and organized not only for other UX designers, but also for developers</h3>
    
            <div  class="h-100 p-2 d-flex flex-column justify-content-center align-items-center">
              <%= image_tag "stylsheet.png", :class => "img-fluid me justify-content-center" %>
            </div>

